Papers of the War Department is a project of the Roy Rosenzweig Center for History and New Media, George Mason University with funding from the National Historical Publications and Records Commission, the American Council of Learned Societies, and the National Endowment for the Humanities.

Descriptive metadata and transcriptions are available for use under the terms of the Creative Commons by Attribution License (4.0). Permissions for use of the document images are held by their original repository.
